FBIS3-31094 "dreeu031_d_94008" FBIS-EEU-94-031 Document Type:Daily Report 15 Feb 1994 SLOVAKIA Kovac, Moravcik Walk Out of Government Session LD1502102794 Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network in Slovak 0900 GMT 15 Feb 94 LD1502102794 Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network in Slovak 0900 GMT 15 Feb 94 Language: Slovak Article Type:BFN [Excerpts] Privatization projects are the main point on the agenda of today's deliberations of the Slovak Government in Bratislava. [passage omitted] Five minutes into the meeting, Deputy Prime MInister Roman Kovac and Minister of Foreign Affairs Jozef Moravcik walked out. According to unconfirmed reports, until their position has been clarified, they will not attend government sessions. Allegedly, Minister Moravcik went on leave.
